---
title: American Plant-Based Mince Chilli Nachos with Double Plant-Based Mayo & Tomato-Corn Salsa
description: We’re doing nachos like no other because they’re veggie-fied with a saucy and spiced plant-based mince that will have your mouth watering. You can go all out with the toppings too like a creamy mayo or tomato and corn salsa.

